      • getParticipantAsync

        public CompletableFuture<MatchEntity.ParticipantEntity> getParticipantAsync(SummonerEntity summonerEntity)
        Gets a CompletableFuture of the Participant corresponding to the given SummonerEntity. Will return null if the summoner was not found. This may occur in unranked games where identity information is not available.
        Parameters:
        summonerEntity - Summoner to find.
        Returns:
        CompletableFuture of ParticipantEntity, or of null if not found.

      • getParticipant

        public MatchEntity.ParticipantEntity getParticipant(SummonerEntity summonerEntity)
        Gets the Participant corresponding to the given SummonerEntity. Will return null if the summoner was not found. This usually occurs in unranked games where identity information is not available and forAccountIdEnc was not provided..
        Parameters:
        summonerEntity - Summoner to find.
        Returns:
        ParticipantEntity, or null if not found.
